title: Mrs. Kristin Hann v. Pee Dee Presbytery
parties: Mrs. Kristin Hann v. Pee Dee Presbytery
source: Case 2023-01: Mrs. Kristin Hann v. Pee Dee Presbytery, M51GA, 2024, 2041
summary: This Case is judicially out of order because the Complainant lacks standing . Because Mrs. Hann is not subject to the jurisdiction of Pee Dee Presbytery her Complaint is out of order and cannot be put in order, and therefore is dismissed.
